\v 13 Abhahiiri bhaan…®, mubhirikiirw…® korereke m Čbh…® bhu ubhwiyagaaruri. Nawe ubhwiyagaaruri bhwanyu bh Čtagirya mutun…® isim Čka y Č  Čbh Čbh…®, nawe mwisakiry…® k Čbh Čs…®…®gi.
